.3. \">Refs 2nd c.AD+</a>]","strongNumber":"G2006","accentedUnicode":"ἐπιτήδειος","shortDef":"needful, necessary, suitableneeded","mediumDef":"needful, necessary, suitableneeded <br /><b>fit, suitable, necessary,</b> <ref='Jas.2.16'>Jas. 2:16</ref>*","stepGloss":"necessary","stepTransliteration":"epitēdeios","count":1,"_es_Definition":"necesario, apropiado","_zh_tw_Definition":"合適的, 必須的 (雅 2:16)","_zh_Definition":"合适的, 必须的 (雅 2:16)","_step_Type":"word","_vi_Definition":"cần thiết","_zh_tw_Gloss":"所需用","_es_Gloss":"necesario","_zh_Gloss":"所需用"}]}